==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trainer
<hw>Train"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
trains; an instructor; especially, one who trains or prepares men,
horses, etc., for exercises requiring physical agility and
strength.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A militiaman when called out for exercise or
discipline.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark> <rj><au>Bartlett.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Training</ent>⟦br⟧
